        </ul>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="animate space-y-6" id="tech-section">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-y-2 items-center justify-between">
          <h2>
            Tech Stack
          </h2>
          <article>
          <p>
            This is a small sample of the technologies I'm already comfortable working with. Like every good developer though, I'm learning new stacks every day. Don't see your stack on here? Let's chat - I can work quickly to get up to speed on whatever stack your team is using. 
