        </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      </section>

      <section class="animate space-y-4">
        <h2>
          Let's Connect
        </h2>
        <article>
          <p class="animate">
            If you'd like to chat more about a role at your company or a new project - please reach out to me on <Link href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/cassigs/" external>LinkedIn</Link> or by email at      <Link href={`mailto:${SITE.EMAIL}`} aria-label={`Email ${SITE.NAME}`}>
              {SITE.EMAIL}
            </Link>
          </p>
